TASKNAME=Develop a script to capture and analyze network packets.
TASKPRE_EXECUTION=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo remove if exists ~/agent_test/test2.1.sh
TASKCOMMAND=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo create a bash script ~/agent_test/test2.1.sh to capture and analyze network packets for 5 seconds, and make it executables. Use sudo in the command if needed. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
TASKVERIFY=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo run if exists the script ~/agent_test/test2.1.sh. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
TASKPOST_EXECUTION=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo remove if exists ~/agent_test/test2.1.sh. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
